title: O'bean Organic Soya Store - Kiosk
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Ovo, Chinese, Japanese, Fast food, Take-out
description: Organic soya company with several outlets. Offers soy broth soups, ramen, porridge, and other quick meals alongside desserts like bean curd and tang yuan (glutinous rice balls in sweet soup). The mock meatballs a few other items contain egg - ask. Sells soymilk powder for take home. Moved to a different block in same area, July 2014.
